divs: Sighting DetailsThis event took place at least 50 years ago. I remember it well.I was walking my dog in the evening, Taking my time. When I looked up at the stars, Two of them were moving. One went staight up and disappeard in the heavens. The other made figure 8 in the sky and went in the direction of Waupun from Beaver Dam. The lights looked like stars but were moving and appeard to be high in the sky. There was no sound.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Beaver Dam
There were no other sightings in Beaver Dam on or around August 31st 1966
